      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need some help writing a rejection email. It's for a candidate who made it all the way to the final round for a software engineer role, but we just decided to go with someone else. Can you give me a template that's polite and empathetic but still professional and firm? We don't want to leave too much room for debate, but we don't want to be jerk about it either.",
